methods.summary: Saves PDF417 to a file based on extension (.png/.webp/.svg/.svgz/.html/.jpg/.bmp/.ppm/.pbm/.pgm/.pam/.xbm/.xpm/.tga/.ico/.pdf/.eps). Defaults to PNG when no extension is provided.
